This is a game of an alternate future based off of a political simulation held by a group of madwomen, men, and general sociopaths. The simulation will attempt to model these events as well as possible with a straight face, but if anything has been misrepresented you may always inform me.

For more information on the Martian political order and its history, you may read more at https://wakefieldinstitute.org/.

